Coppolaro, M., Moccia, M., Castaldi, G., Engheta, N., &amp; Galdi, V. (2019). Non-Hermitian doping of epsilon-near-zero media. In USNC-URSI Radio Science Meeting. Atlanta, GA, USA, July 7-12, 2019.
